HEADWORD: Upcountry
<hw>Up"coun`try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an upcountry
direction; <as>as, to live <ex>upcountry</ex></as>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

