==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Upcountry
<hw>Up"coun`try</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Living or situated remote from
the seacoast; <as>as, an <ex>upcountry</ex> residence</as>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The interior of the
country.</def></def2> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Upcurl</ent>⟦br⟧
